# TDD Development Workflow — Nutrition Intelligence Agent

## Context
- Project: Nutrition Intelligence Agent
- Stack: C# .NET 10, Minimal API, rule-based Nutrition Scoring Engine
- External API: Open Food Facts v2 product read + Search-a-licious for alternatives (no key needed)
- Scoring: deterministic C# rules — sugar, fat, saturated fat, protein, fiber, salt per 100g
- No LLM, no Semantic Kernel, no API keys required

## Tools Available
- fetch MCP → call Open Food Facts API
- filesystem MCP → read/write project files
- Playwright MCP → test HTTP endpoints
- openspec → generate OpenAPI docs

---

## Phase 1: Planning
BMAD đã chạy xong. Artifacts ở `_bmad-output/planning-artifacts/`.
Đọc PRD + Architecture + Stories trước khi làm bất cứ thứ gì.

