## Phase 2: Verify API Shape
Trước khi viết bất kỳ C# model nào, dùng fetch MCP:
GET https://world.openfoodfacts.org/api/v2/product/3017620422003.json
GET https://world.openfoodfacts.org/api/v2/product/5000159407236.json
GET https://search.openfoodfacts.org/search?q=confectionary+based+spreads&page_size=3&fields=code,product_name,nutriscore_grade

Map fields thật vào models. Không đoán mò.

Checklist nutriments (per 100g):
- [ ] `sugars_100g`, `fat_100g`, `saturated-fat_100g`, `proteins_100g`, `fiber_100g`, `salt_100g`
- [ ] `nutriscore_grade`, `categories_tags`, `product_name`, `brands`, `ingredients_text`
- [ ] Note fields nullable vs required

