## Phase 5: Code Review
**Trace:** Update `docs/verification/{story-key}.md` — record reviewer model (khác implementer), date, outcome. Index: `docs/VERIFICATION.md`.

Checklist trước khi báo done:
- [ ] Tests XANH
- [ ] Không bare try/catch
- [ ] Không hardcode OFF response
- [ ] Scoring logic deterministic (same input → same output)
- [ ] `nutritionInsights` có disclaimer field
- [ ] `GET /products/{barcode}` không có `alternatives` array

---

## Phase 6: Integration Test (Playwright MCP)
**Trace:** Ghi kết quả vào cùng file `docs/verification/{story-key}.md` (paste output). N/A nếu story chưa có HTTP endpoint.

Sau khi `dotnet run` thành công, chạy Playwright MCP:
- [ ] GET /products/3017620422003 → 200 + nutritionInsights non-empty
- [ ] GET /products/invalid → 404
- [ ] GET /products/3017620422003/alternatives → 200 + array non-empty
- [ ] nutritionInsights.disclaimer non-empty
- [ ] Response có nutritionScore + healthBand

